<h3 style="text-align: left;"><img src="/media/13086966/site_masthead_chalet.jpg" alt="Inghams Chalets" data-udi="umb://media/dfaefa21358048d88db8a58b5b65a72a" /></h3>
<h2>Inghams catered ski chalets</h2>
<p>Our catered ski chalets are the perfect base for your alpine holiday. Your chalet hosts will be ready to help you with all aspects of your holiday and make your stay as comfortable as possible. Cosy with warm and welcoming furnishings and décor, our ski chalets feature all the comforts of home. Full of thoughtful touches, each chalet boasts an inviting atmosphere and plenty of space to relax after a day on the slopes.</p>
<p>Most Chalet Hosts are also avid skiers or snowboarders, and love to share their knowledge and passion for the slopes with our guests. </p>
<p>You can expect plenty of home-cooked comfort food to fuel your ski days, so all you have to do is get up and go skiing. Our larger chalets have a professional chalet chef to cook for you, with chalet assistants helping to serve all meals and look after the chalet’s house-keeping duties.</p>
<p>Our Chalet service offering includes: </p>
<ul>
<li>Continental breakfast for 7 mornings with hot options provided by your chalet host on 6 days</li>
<li>Afternoon tea and cake (6 days)</li>
<li>6 days of Prosecco apéritif before dinner (6 days)</li>
<li>3 course set menu evening meal including a special regional menu on one night (6 days)</li>
<li>Unlimited wine, red, white and rosé to enjoy during your evening meal</li>
<li>This season, our chalets are going greener so our mountains don't - read more below</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div></div>
<div>
<h2>Ski chalets in Europe:</h2>
<p>Find your ideal ski chalet for your next skiing holiday this winter, with a wide selection to choose from across European resorts: </p>
