<p><img src="/media/13098020/chalet-kapall-500x250.jpg" alt="chaletkapall" data-udi="umb://media/3bc71450596c4f718ee1bd1c9f80ce4f" /></p>
<p>Relax in front of the chalet’s log fire and enjoy chalet catering, along with the excellent wellness facility, including an indoor plunge pool and sauna.</p>
</div>
