<h2>France</h2>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/f086bd745df54ae9944d84f9e210cec5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f086bd745df54ae9944d84f9e210cec5}" title="Chalet Secret de Neige">Chalet Secret de Neige</a></h3>
<p><strong>Alpe d'Huez</strong></p>
<p><img src="/media/13098028/chalet-secret-de-neige-500x250.jpg" alt="chaletsecret" data-udi="umb://media/73a64e1e997d4394a55de6903984a889" /></p>
<p>With its fantastic location it's hard to beat, not to mention the modern interiors and wooden architecture that reflects its traditional French alpine roots.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
