<p><strong>Avoriaz</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2411c782bdc14ac48c17ef706cce6dc8}" title="Chalet Marie"><img src="/media/13092215/chalet-marie-314x193.jpg" alt="Chalet Marie" data-udi="umb://media/1e451fc0d4974133ad8d8042c6337876" /></a></p>
