<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This popular chalet offers seven bedrooms, furnished to a high standard with en-suites. Sip your morning coffee from the sun terrace with spectacular views. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925" href="/{localLink:umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925}" title="Chalet Mathilde">Chalet Mathilde</a></h3>
<p><strong>Val Thorens</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925" href="/{localLink:umb://document/65b4a42a6b4a41abbeb1d855ba97c925}" title="Chalet Mathilde"><img src="/media/13092305/chalet-mathilde-314x193.jpg" alt="Chalet Mathilde" data-udi="umb://media/378308add2dc4291b3f26e843e46aa9d" /></a></p>
<p>The spacious chalet features a sun terrace, sauna,  steam room and cosy lounge area with log burning stove. <span>You can ski or walk 100 metres along a track to the piste.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d71c920311ae410ebf6c3d6d217d6cc2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d71c920311ae410ebf6c3d6d217d6cc2}" title="Chalet La Breche">Chalet La Breche - </a>Alpe d'Huez</p>
This 16 bed chalet has one of the best locations in Alpe d'Huez, just to the side of the piste close to the 'Telecentre' lift.</div>
<div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/1de1d81241e3469f8b30346a82c00993" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1de1d81241e3469f8b30346a82c00993}" title="Chalet L'Ancolie">Chalet L'Ancolie - </a>Méribel</p>
<p>This superb chalet was built in traditional Savoyard style, in a quiet location and set back and slightly above the main road, offering good mountain views.</p>
</div>
<div>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/0f5433ea301c4a629e7b0da9f972c6e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0f5433ea301c4a629e7b0da9f972c6e5}" title="Chalet Cairn">Chalet Cairn - </a>Tignes</p>
<p>Chalet Cairn has a stunning location on the lakeshore in Tignes and is a stylish and comfortable property sleeping up to 14 people with six bedrooms.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/66ca5d10cae64be8b9b5fb73ed58606d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/66ca5d10cae64be8b9b5fb73ed58606d}" title="Chalet Noella">Chalet Noella - </a>Val Thorens</p>
<p>Chalet Noella is ideally located, with the nearest piste is just 100 metres away and, to relax after skiing, there's a shared sauna and steam room to enjoy.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/50d7f9d96e7c4638bdcc2e69478973f1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/50d7f9d96e7c4638bdcc2e69478973f1}" title="Chalet Chloe">Chalet Chloe - </a>Val Thorens</p>
<p>Chalet Chloe is one three Inghams chalets in a small residence just by the Balcons area of Val Thorens with a 100 metres walk connecting to the Plein Sud piste.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e611fe310a444e08a8b57c6b19dad7e4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e611fe310a444e08a8b57c6b19dad7e4}" title="Chalet Corniche">Chalet Corniche - </a>Tignes</p>
<p>A family-friendly, contemporary style property with a sun terrace, steam room and hot tub, offering impressive views of the mountains.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bc23c629c2294dfb837ab6a087f45bee" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bc23c629c2294dfb837ab6a087f45bee}" title="Chalet Le Cedre Blanc">Chalet Le Cedre Blanc - </a>Méribel</p>
<p>Chalet Le Cedre Blanc is a high quality chalet that offers a wonderful place to relax after a day skiing the extensive Three Valleys.</p>
</div>
